widget.name: ListSorter
widget.description: Add a header to your list view or template grid with interactive sorting on click.

property.caption: Header CSS Class
property.description: Zero or more CSS classes to apply to the header label. Uses spaces to separate.

property.caption: List Widget Name
property.description: The name of the list view or template grid to target

property.caption: List Entity
property.description: The type of objects in the list.

property.caption: Sorting Attribute
property.description: The attribute to sort on the grid.
